{"id":181874,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":3,"day":30}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"美术周刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"290","ytitle":"","mtitle":"一家老少垂间人","ftitle":"","authors":["施文起"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\03\\503u060801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>施文起作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农事将作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"检查一下农具是否需要添新补旧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲弓着背，编筐篓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜倚着烟杆，倦了抽他几口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说:这种轻松工作该让我来干。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\03\\503u060802.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>好的种子才长得出好的果实:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲卷着大袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选佳种，漂稗子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证田里不长一株稗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风调雨顺等丰收。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\03\\503u060803.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>三月天，新雨初收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟儿声声催割谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥做事有计划，从不落人后。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁闲时拌好堆肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"省得临时忙手忙足。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\03\\503u060804.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>多少年了，家里没有养过猪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，今年栏里热闹了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂既忙家事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又定时一天喂它们三次。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她抹着汗珠“田里的肥料有了着落”。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\03\\503u060805.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>别看轻这条牛，耕田磨粉全靠它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃厌了干料，现在可以尝到青草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟一天到晚伴着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期望它长得更高更大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了干自家事，还可以帮忙人家。</FONT>"}]}